{"tid":343282,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"你班契弟仲唔科水！熱狗仔隊倒蝕喇！","createTime":"2017-08-01T10:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T18:17:30.000Z","uid":103230,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"532f05c12241f76d6545a157ce8a30a41d3027fa","tid":343282,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/181215_da5a513cf8d2cb9c0c017a2c50d56dd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F181215_da5a513cf8d2cb9c0c017a2c50d56dd2.jpg&h=f0c9eb59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越黎越相信熱狗仔隊只係鳩達cap水既一個項目<br />\n囉黎貼熱狗營運同自肥<br />\n<br />\n七一乞唔到錢同火鳳tee滯銷<br />\n書展幾十萬蟹貨同場租<br />\n搞個唔知有冇人去既天才表演show<br />\n蝕到仆街<br />\n<br />\n而家又黎同人講熱仔隊唔夠錢<br />\n有冇咁啱呀⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e1d666ce9a696e7e7230acc4f17bc085b0e0e0","tid":343282,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:20:08.000Z","msg":"半年可以蝕到194萬<br />\n<br />\n現時估計熱狗約有300萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6896da78b72eb22c2d2cfa21b3ee8e5705d337","tid":343282,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>半年可以蝕到194萬<br />\n<br />\n現時估計熱狗約有300萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as